	Weatherman: {
		DisplayName: Weatherman

		TownNPCMood: {
			Content: I'm pretty happy here!
			NoHome: I need some shelter, preferably in the jungle.
			FarFromHome: I gotta get back home before it rains!
			LoveSpace: Nice, plenty of privacy to tinker with new forecast devices!
			DislikeCrowded: It's a little crammed for me around here.
			HateCrowded: There's way too many people around!
			LikeBiome: I love when it rains here in the jungle. It's like a real Rainforest Cafe!
			DislikeBiome: The desert is so dry! Not enough weather for my taste.
			HateBiome: I hate not being able to experience the weather.
			LoveNPC: When making my forecast devices, {NPCName} was such a good partner.
			LikeNPC: I like how much {NPCName} appreciates the weather.
			DislikeNPC: "{NPCName} doesn't like the weather, so I don't like him!"
			HateNPC: I think {NPCName} charges too much, I don't get paid enough for this!
			LikeNPC_Princess: I enjoy talking to {NPCName}, she reminds me of my daughter.
			Princess_LovesNPC: I enjoy talking to {NPCName}, she reminds me of my daughter.
		}

		DeathMessage: The weatherman was slain...
	}

	LivingSunflower.DisplayName: Living Sunflower
	Snake.DisplayName: Snake
	AngrySun.DisplayName: Angry Sun
}

