Tiles.SunshineInABottle.MapEntry: Sunshine in a Bottle

Dialogue: {
	Weatherman: {
		Normal1: I'm loving the weather today! Well, I do most days.
		Normal2: The mechanic was a big help when making my forecast devices. I couldn't have done it without her!
		Normal3: Have you seen me on the news? I got to keep the microphone!
		Rain1: Make sure to grab an umbrella on your way out.
		Rain2: Oh crap, where's my umbrella? I thought I left it right here!
		WindyDay1: Today would be a great day to fly my kite!
		WindyDay2: Watch out for slimes today, I saw one being carried by a balloon!
		Thunderstorm1: Ah, I love the sounds of a thunderstorm.
		Thunderstorm2: Get in here! It's storming hard!
		SunnyDay1: It's so sunny today! Don't forget to use sunscreen.
		SunnyDay2: I wouldn't wanna be a vampire today!
		SlimeRain1: Never seen weather like this before.
		SlimeRain2: How does this weather even make sense?
		Underground1: I can't experience the weather down here!
		Underground2: Is there another house for me on the surface? I don't wanna miss out on the weather.
		Underworld1: Why am I all the way down here? Do you just hate me or something?
		Underworld2: The temperatures down here are crazy!
	}
}

Bestiary.Weatherman: The Weatherman used to be just a typical meteorologist and news anchor, but after working with the mechanic, he's learned to control the weather itself!

BossChecklistIntegration: {
	BuriedBarrageInvasion: {
		EntryName: Buried Barrage
		SpawnInfo: Summoned with a Mutated Heart in the caverns. Mutated Hearts can be found in gold chests underground.
	}
}
